    Major changes between "nagios-plugins-uptime" versions 5 and 6

* Rework help and version messages.
* COPYING: update to GPLv3. 
* Code refactoring.

======================================================================

    Major changes between "nagios-plugins-uptime" versions 4 and 5

* Add support for Solaris 11 x86 (SunOS solaris 5.11 11.1, gcc 4.5.2).

======================================================================

    Major changes between "nagios-plugins-uptime" versions 3 and 4

* Add support for AIX (6.1 with gcc 4.2.0).

======================================================================

    Major changes between "nagios-plugins-uptime" versions 2 and 3

* The plugin "nagios-plugins-linux-uptime" has been renamed to
  "nagios-plugins-uptime".
* Add support for FreeBSD (8.2-RELEASE-p10).
* Add perfdata to the plugin output.
* Update package documentation.

======================================================================

 Major changes between "nagios-plugins-linux-uptime" versions 1 and 2

* Autotoolize package build.
* Enable more compiler warnings when using gcc.

======================================================================
